						<summary>

						<p>This is in modern characters and is dated in Krōdhana, Tai. It mentions some order (not clear) of the committee of the Vīrabhadrasvāmi temple, during the regime (<hi rend="italic">pārapatyam</hi>) of Nāgarasayyar, the agent of Tāṇḍavamuttu-śeṭṭiyār.</p>						

